        void resourcesChanged(java.util.Collection resources)
        Notify that some watched resources were changed.

        It is permitted to receive empty collection of resources.

        See IWatchableRepository for more information of what changes and how can be reported.

        Parameters:
        resources - Collection of IWatchableRepositoryListener.IChangedResources
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if locations is null
